quotedTweet.rawContent:
@Positive_Call Doing the opposite of what depression wants. 

So, when depression wants you to:

• Stay in bed, you get up
• Skip showering, you shower
• Stay indoors, you go for a walk
• Isolate yourself, you phone someone
• Leave the washing, you do the washing

Simple, but not easy.
